CMPT 355 — Individual Project
 

Package cmpt355.project.codegen

Classes related to the code generation part of the compiler.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CodeGenerator
    A class that generates JVM assembly code from an AST.
    CompileContext
    The main class used when generating JVM assembly code.
    Helper
    A class that provides helpful shortcuts for common operations in JVM assembly.
    Label
    A class representing a label in assembly code: something that can be branched by to another instruction such as Instruction.new_goto(InstructionAddressOperand).
